  • Method Details

    • createBooking

      void createBooking(int bookingId, int userId, int slotId, String bookingDate, String bookingTimeSlotStart, String bookingTimeSlotEnd, int bookingStatus, int transactionId, int bookingAmount)
      Creates a new booking in the gym system.
      Parameters:
      bookingId - The unique identifier for the booking.
      userId - The ID of the user making the booking.
      slotId - The ID of the time slot for the booking.
      bookingDate - The date of the booking in string format.
      bookingTimeSlotStart - The start time of the booking time slot in string format.
      bookingTimeSlotEnd - The end time of the booking time slot in string format.
      bookingStatus - The status of the booking (e.g., confirmed, pending).
      transactionId - The ID of the transaction associated with the booking.
      bookingAmount - The amount paid for the booking (if applicable).
